title: Airport Mania First Flight - Dash Game (Requested) [h33t][Wendy9
description:
Pack your bags for an exciting trip as you take to the skies and 

journey from airport to airport helping customers along the way! Each 

of the eight locations you&#039;ll fly to features unique challenges and 

whimsical planes. Upgrade your airport along the way with larger 

planes, painting spaces and in -flight movies to keep your customers 

happy, and be sure to avoid any delays!
Game features:
Travel to 8 airports!
Flying fun for everyone!
Enjoy 84 unique Levels!
Customize your own Airport!
Earn over 20 awards!
Whimsical Graphics and Music!
Secret Paper planes mode!
System requirements:
Windows of 98/.ME/2000/XP/Vista
DirectX 8
700 mHz
128 mb RAM
